{"tid":1176194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次有圖 女工搭升降機玩手機　耳機線遭閘門拉扯斷頭死","createTime":"2019-05-29T04:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T02:04:26.000Z","uid":72009,"like":247,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"32306efacf1921acc66fce0551c3c170334538b1","tid":1176194,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"印度古吉拉特邦瓦多達拉一名工廠女工，周一（27日）乘搭升降機時，疑因接連手機的耳機線纏在升降機的拉閘，意外將她拉去閘門，最終慘遭斬首死亡。她的頭部跌在地下，屍身則被扯上其他樓層。 <br />\n<br />\n48歲的維什沃克默（Sushila Vishwakarma）當日上午如常上班，由地下乘搭升降機前往工作樓層，結果身首異處。當地警方懷疑，維什沃克默戴着的耳機線與拉閘纏在一起，結果導致慘劇發生。據報她的屍首已被消防員尋回，並已移交其家人。 <br />\n<br />\n當地官員至今仍未清楚事故成因，已將案件列為意外死亡，目前正在等待驗屍結果。另有一名警員懷疑，維什沃克默可能是因為玩手機而分心，結果在升降機上移時，誤將頭部伸出閘門，最終造成慘劇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190529/mobile/bkn-20190529040026156-0529_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190529%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190529040026156-0529_00912_001.html&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1Ls4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=e020f40e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190529/mobile/bkn-20190529040026156-0529_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190529/photo/bkn-20190529040026156-0529_00912_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190529%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190529040026156-0529_00912_001_01p.jpg&h=e5fcd24e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不求高清無碼圖"},{"pid":"3ca0d3000362e2a817dff64b5218f82e428fb5b8","tid":1176194,"uid":173606,"like":51,"dislike":252,"score":-201,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"呢d又無高清圖睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794a7722363cb512be734e2e2808d062f1d4d2ef","tid":1176194,"uid":196924,"like":681,"dislike":18,"score":663,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"耳機線邊有咁硬淨<br />\n就算條線硬，個耳塞都甩啦<br />\n<br />\n不過啲印狗好似好鐘意咬住個收音咪<br />\n可能真係纏實咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8293868f9bf665fd1e90be76eb6cb9fe2241be7","tid":1176194,"uid":168730,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"圖?"},{"pid":"3fd5704ebfc1949fafc725074166af79fa668c72","tid":1176194,"uid":64009,"like":37,"dislike":9,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:54:03.000Z","msg":"無碼圖呢屌你"},{"pid":"85adff0f77778e0a700b3ac0bed19305191559e4","tid":1176194,"uid":59030,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:54:11.000Z","msg":"一抆就斷整得死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f2f26c7244b6dc52371cda8279de54c034f8ea","tid":1176194,"uid":34836,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:54:52.000Z","msg":"死神來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420b590df7578d2971459f6481326f0faae62bc4","tid":1176194,"uid":196735,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"耳機線咁硬淨"},{"pid":"591ce739c80c22a82b10f060201c92756e7fee76","tid":1176194,"uid":152726,"like":490,"dislike":2,"score":488,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:01:48.000Z","msg":"原來我之前用咁多易斷既線係無咁易斬首。D廠真係有良心"},{"pid":"426cbf92d3fd6d74f1cc4d94d4257f1f211fe394","tid":1176194,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:03:21.000Z","msg":"廢老：抵死，掛住玩手機"},{"pid":"49d59ca2d60864cd4d79caf46bae12a303700811","tid":1176194,"uid":57677,"like":113,"dislike":9,"score":104,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"fake news, 少少力都會斷<br />\n<br />\n除非十萬元級"},{"pid":"a843f24be0609c7c6d9ee49c585cd721618cbe5f","tid":1176194,"uid":253170,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:05:19.000Z","msg":"有無得求耳機線牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bc479517f46c3c3538e56af504a1d96cd262d7","tid":1176194,"uid":10635,"like":133,"dislike":1,"sco